targets.rawSql:
SELECT $__timeInterval(query_start_time) as time,
       normalizeQuery(query) AS normalized_query,
       query_duration_ms
FROM system.query_log
WHERE normalized_query NOT ILIKE 'INSERT INTO%' AND normalized_query LIKE '%livenx_flowdb%' AND type != 'QueryStart' AND $__timeFilter(event_time)
ORDER BY time

panels.title: LiveNX FlowDB Query performance over time

targets.rawSql:
SELECT $__timeInterval(query_start_time) as time,
       normalizeQuery(query) AS normalized_query,
       query_duration_ms
FROM system.query_log
WHERE type != 'QueryStart' AND query LIKE '%SELECT toStartOfMinute%'
  AND $__timeFilter(event_time)
ORDER BY time
